msgstr ""

#. type: table
#: guix-git/doc/guix.texi:27164
msgid "See the hpcguix-web repository for a @uref{https://github.com/UMCUGenetics/hpcguix-web/blob/master/hpcweb-configuration.scm, complete example}."
